-    Higher Education Graduates in the Labor Market in Romania, proceedings of the Conference “New Horizons in Industry, Business and Education” – NHIBE 2011, Chios, Greece, 2011. 
-    The Shift to a Learning Outcomes in Qualifications for the Air Transport Industry, proceedings of the Conference “New Horizons in Industry, Business and Education” – NHIBE 2011, Chios, Grèce, 2011 
